e want to use)\n\nparam context_len\n\nint\nAmount of desired token context for prediction. Needs to be at least 1.\n\nparam prefix_token\n\ntoken\nDummy token like <eos> so the first token has something to condition on\n\nreturn\n\ngenerator\nGenerator of tuples\n\nsource:14: (ERROR/3) Unexpected indentation.\n\n(input_tokens, pred_tokens)\n\nsource:15: (WARNING/2) Block quote ends without a blank line; unexpected unindent.\n\nNote: Score only the last len(pred_tokens) logits of the LM\n```\n"]}, {"name": "hflm.utils.make_disjoint_window", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "pair", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "hflm.utils.stop_sequences_criteria", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "tokenizer", "type": {"name": "transformers.PreTrainedTokenizer", "xref": {"fqname": "transformers.PreTrainedTokenizer", "project": "transformers"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "stop_sequences", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "initial_decoder_input_length", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "batch_size", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "transformers.StoppingCriteriaList", "xref": {"fqname": "transformers.StoppingCriteriaList", "project": "transformers"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "hflm.utils.pad_and_concat", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "max_length", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "tensors", "type": {"name": "List", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.List", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "torch.T